M&R, Al Habtoor Get $600 Million Abu Dhabi Hospital Contract

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-15T12:44:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/m-r-al-habtoor-get-600-million-abu-dhabi-hospital-contract.html
Murray & Roberts Ltd. and Al
Habtoor Leighton Group won a 2.2 billion-dirham ($600 million)
contract for the construction of a hospital in Abu Dhabi, the
Johannesburg-based construction company said in a statement on
its website today.  Click here for the Company Statement  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
